# Security headers (Cloudflare Pages, Netlify-style).
# Conservative set — no CSP, since the site relies on inline scripts/styles
# and a strict CSP would risk breaking them. These improve scanner ratings
# and signal a legitimate, well-configured site. They do NOT fix
# newly-registered-domain firewall blocks (submit the domain for
# categorization with the major vendors for that).

/*
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains; preload
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), microphone=(), camera=(), payment=()
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
